verbose_text: Consistent with these findings, quantitative immunogold analyses confirmed that a well characterized VMAT2 signal, was present in the layer 5 (L5) mPFC astrocytic processes of P30 rats recognized for the expression of GLT1 / GLAST25 or GS, although the density of gold particles was about 3 fold less than in DAergic axons but still significantly above background (+82%) calculated in mitochondria (n = 3 rats; one-way ANOVA, Bonferroni 's post-test correction, * p < 0.05).
